#: ../content/index.rst:25
msgid "Usage"
msgstr ""

#: ../content/index.rst:26
msgid "Editing of subject, body and attachments in general is already possible for internal notes. With this package, editing can be enabled for phone and email articles as well, alongside with editing further article attributes like customer visibility state, adding time units and editing article dynamic field values."
msgstr ""

#: ../content/index.rst:28
msgid "Editing subject, body and attachments can be en- or disabled for internal and phone articles and is in general not possible for e-mail articles."
msgstr ""

#: ../content/index.rst:30
msgid "Editing an article without having enabled editing subject, body and attachments may look like figure 3.1."
msgstr ""

