#: ../content/index.rst:36
msgid "The screenshot shows an article edit screen without subject, body and attachments."
msgstr ""

#: ../content/index.rst:38
msgid "Editing an article for which editing of subject, body and attachments is enabled may look like figure 3.2."
msgstr ""

